@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = v1
    tmp = ((0.04 - wp.exp(v2 + 0.01)) / wp.exp((tmp + 0.02 * v0 + 0.89)))
    v1 = wp.exp(((tmp + 0.53 / v1 + 0.81) - wp.sin(v1 + 0.41)))
    tmp = wp.exp(wp.cos(0.65))
    v0 = 0.02
    v2 = tmp
    v0 = 0.27
    tmp = 0.86
    data[tid] = v0
